Dear Hiring Team, 

It is with great pleasure that I submit my candidacy for the *Java Developer* position with *Morgan Stanley*. I bring over three years of professional experience in enterprise server-side applications using Java, Spring Boot, and Hibernate, along with a strong academic foundation as a Master of Science in Computer Science graduate from Pace University, NY with a 4.0 GPA.

