I have always been passionate about delivering the right solutions to clients and managing business with a long-term perspective, and envision myself contributing my talent to the furthering of Morgan Stanley's mission to create a world-class financial services firm. I would love to discuss my interest in this position with your team and can be reached at #ph or #eml. Thank you for your time and consideration, I look forward to connecting!

